# .trivyignore
# Unfixable OS-level CVEs in python:3.12-slim (debian 13.4)
# No fix available from Debian upstream as of 2025-05-03
# These are suppressed pending upstream patch release
# Review date: 2025-08-03

# libcap2 — TOCTOU race in cap_set_file()
# Impact: requires local access + specific file operations — not reachable in containerised Flask app
CVE-2026-4878

# ncurses — buffer overflow
# Impact: ncurses is not used by the application at runtime
CVE-2025-69720

# systemd/udev — IPC code execution
# Impact: systemd is not the init system inside the container; udev is not active
CVE-2026-29111